        "timestamp": "2019-11-12 07:12:58.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\n> Patch Set 4:\n> \n> (2 comments)\n> \n> In addition to my comments below, please try to implement more robust solution -\n> There's a potential issue with more than one user testing the same VSP, they can override each other test results. \n> Also, a better solution is to query VTP for possible test results, keeping SDC stateless, rather than storing an identifier per VSP id/version.\n\n\nHI Ofir,\n\nAs discussed in the weekly meeting on 11/11/2019, Vodafone team will add userid in SDC database table along with VSPid and version id to make result's identifier unique according to user.",
        "patchset_number": 4
