        "message": "Patch Set 5: Code-Review-1\n\nHi Atul - can you please investigate the option to implement it in this release? I don't like the idea that SDC keeps state information, many teams worked hard to keep it stateless.\n\nYou're also welcome to suggest another solution instead, so it stays stateless.\n\nI wouldn't like to merge a feature that has a flaw in its design, nor to postpone fixes/refactoring to futures releases.",
